    "rating": 5,
    "subject": "Lovely to See Emma Regularly",
    "comments": "Emma has been visiting me more often and it means the world to me, especially with my diagnosis. The staff are always so accommodating with family time and make sure Emma can see us whenever she wants. She seems much happier and more confident. Thank you for taking such good care of my granddaughter.",
